    "(3) Five to eight articles were randomly selected in each subgroup.",
    "(4) Only the articles with more than one variant entity were chosen.",
    "The interested articles were then annotated with PTC [19], serving as the initial corpus for manual annotation to facilitate our annotating speed.",
    "In the early stage of our annotation, the strategy of three-person manual annotation was adopted.",
    "Specifically, the same batch of articles were assigned to two annotators independently."
